@startuml
title URL检测时序图

actor Client as "前端页面"
participant API as "Django后端"
participant Engine as "检测引擎"
database DB as "SQLite数据库"

Client -> API: POST /api/detection/detect-url/
note right: {"url": "https://phishing.example.com"}
API -> DB: 查询钓鱼特征库
DB --> API: 返回所有URL特征
API -> Engine: 执行特征匹配
Engine -> Engine: 计算置信度
Engine --> API: 返回检测结果
API -> DB: 保存检测记录
DB --> API: 保存成功
API --> Client: 200 OK

@enduml
